
** Steps to define a Xref source

** Xref-Manual

*** Specify the source

  - (region) *H-q r* specify a source

*** Specify the target

  - (region) *H-q C-r* specify a target
  -          *H-q SPC* specify a buffer-file-name as target
  -      *C-u H-q SPC* specify a file as target
  -          *H-q @*   specify a action as target

